{"tid":210903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連登絲打剪錯毛　靚貓即變草泥馬","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T13:26:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63fb898161c1ddd89c593278b92edff1444a60cf","tid":210903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/funky/img/2017-04/20/7784/keithyim_1_9e0f058982268de9c8c0322812537e01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Ffunky%2Fimg%2F2017-04%2F20%2F7784%2Fkeithyim_1_9e0f058982268de9c8c0322812537e01.jpg&h=cccad1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港開始天氣熱，唔少奴才都會幫下主子去清理下毛，希望主子可以呢個夏天過得舒服少少，話說 「LiHK 連登」有位叫「絲 CUP 悲 B」絲打近日幫屋企隻貓剪毛，點知剪到真係出曬事咁。<br />\n<br />\n事前<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/funky/img/2017-04/20/7784/wilsonhms_1_d756cf3bfa4e2c2ad05bb57c23b46396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Ffunky%2Fimg%2F2017-04%2F20%2F7784%2Fwilsonhms_1_d756cf3bfa4e2c2ad05bb57c23b46396.jpg&h=1688f68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎奴才今次出事啦，剪到自己個主子剪到成個草泥馬咁，今次要買返 D 罐罐補數啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/18/7784/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Ffun%2Ftalk%2F18%2F7784%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4180c35e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/18/7784/</a>"},{"pid":"e6385a4f57e274662cdf7941d95fa6b133d80a96","tid":210903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"事後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/funky/img/2017-04/20/7784/wilsonhms_1_515aa8fde8c196d53af2a5cbed5612cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Ffunky%2Fimg%2F2017-04%2F20%2F7784%2Fwilsonhms_1_515aa8fde8c196d53af2a5cbed5612cb.jpg&h=b4c947ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed6cc2897552812c